{"tid":1249333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"來自警察妻子的肺腑之言","createTime":"2019-06-21T16:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T04:07:27.000Z","uid":265019,"like":2659,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"710345408650868b2d2d131e9394ff510db57fde","tid":1249333,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我和Ken結了婚五年，我們是大學同學，他在警總。<br />\n做警察是他的志願。<br />\n十二點，我等他回家，他說被示威者包圍，今天不能見面。<br />\n最近他很忙，忙著應付示威的事情。<br />\n他回家時會痛罵處長，說他瘋了，罵他推前線去死。<br />\n有晚我醒了，他不在我身旁，獨自在廳看新聞。<br />\n他看到我，然後哭。<br />\n<br />\n我看著電視，警總外人潮如鯽。<br />\n我心情忐忑，學生的訴求其實也是警察的訴求：<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會，還前線警員一個清白。<br />\n政府只要一聲令下，他便可以回家。<br />\n<br />\nKen說當了五年警察，心累了，想辭職，做一個平凡、正直的人，但要供樓。<br />\n我希望看到他一展愁顏，但無情的政府，似乎卻要讓他抱恨終身......</span>"},{"pid":"3b3e99d2657083dac8208b2151e1c49203f6317c","tid":1249333,"uid":265019,"like":257,"dislike":2,"score":255,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"認同請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cbf70c701bcd7fb07ce60e95673e64e7edf713","tid":1249333,"uid":265019,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091227cc09f08ad0184c90ffa9a720afb410a598","tid":1249333,"uid":155493,"like":473,"dislike":19,"score":454,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"又阿媽又老婆 你都好忙下 5年咁快有個大仔做警察"},{"pid":"fbb92c02520ffc9a1c8ce73b81982fddd3e8d279","tid":1249333,"uid":369,"like":432,"dislike":3,"score":429,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"h