dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />還佢地清白"},{"pid":"15479921574330bb279e4376d1b12e91ddb1213b","tid":1249333,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5306261fc0dd311020580f94df09452b61a7e820","tid":1249333,"uid":87511,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:31:47.000Z","msg":"咪戇鳩<br />\n收到風，阿Ken今日下晝12點已經換哂便裝走撚咗<br />\n之後化身特別職務隊，show pass叫霸王雞"},{"pid":"d1a539c25c3fffdf62760abfd6ebb8b597e168f3","tid":1249333,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成立獨立調查委員會！！！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"db3028921223409b2925060559859f34b17a9b48","tid":1249333,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:32:11.000Z","msg":"冇錢學咩人買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99b0b1ea247c3835398590689b39ab01f29bc24","tid":1249333,"uid":61789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:32:53.000Z","msg":"有冇多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8865c6223931c20ab55c93425efbaa8108e16f78","tid":1249333,"uid":259156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:33:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"315dbeba63336dac30b35f98c30c3ecfb4d6045f","tid":1249333,"uid":43904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"710345408650868b2d2d131e9394ff510db57fde","tid":1249333,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我和Ken結了婚五年，我們是大學同學，他在警總。<br />\n做警察是他的志願。<br />\n十二點，我等他回家，他說被示威者包圍，今天不能見面。<br />\n最近他很忙，忙著應付示威的事情。<br />\n他回家時會痛罵處長，說他瘋了，罵他推前線去死。<br />\n有晚我醒了，他不在我身旁，獨自在廳看新聞。<br />\n他看到我，然後哭。<br />\n<br />\n我看著電視，警總外人潮如鯽。<br />\n我心情忐忑，學生的訴求其實也是警察的訴求：<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會，還前線警員一個清白。<br />\n政府只要一聲令下，他便可以回家。<br />\n<br />\nKen說當了五年警察，心累了，想辭職，做一個平凡、正直的人，但要供樓。<br />\n我希望看到他一展愁顏，但無情的政府，似乎卻要讓他抱恨終身......</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:34:21.000Z","msg":"香港得警察做？大撚把窮人都生活到，可以賴邊個？供樓大晒？"},{"pid":"4161844e754ac811e39762834da38f87e3c2bd96","tid":1249333,"uid":43904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019f27437775da3c748a4cadab22171dcb0b363a","tid":1249333,"uid":265019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2df9e83a1cad147b05adfdb9587e62405aaad035","tid":1249333,"uid":14238,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5G2sksR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5G2sksR.png&h=af5069a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"好圖！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:35:14.000Z","msg":"要警醒"},{"pid":"5ce905dc65be37b48edbe3ce0c55b9511a5858a0","tid":1249333,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不推不是人"},{"pid":"f4118b93f78f0be381d0c1fbe31d8a0a456034f9","tid":1249333,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d07e5339cb83175e47e0a124a43b530847891fa9","tid":1249333,"uid":158766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1368f4fe28de