class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73d4c0b2b92d9c58214a1a8ac02572030191268","tid":1249333,"uid":94819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e8d6ffadfaa5b461fada52e17068a2849ada714","tid":1249333,"uid":51340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"710345408650868b2d2d131e9394ff510db57fde","tid":1249333,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我和Ken結了婚五年，我們是大學同學，他在警總。<br />\n做警察是他的志願。<br />\n十二點，我等他回家，他說被示威者包圍，今天不能見面。<br />\n最近他很忙，忙著應付示威的事情。<br />\n他回家時會痛罵處長，說他瘋了，罵他推前線去死。<br />\n有晚我醒了，他不在我身旁，獨自在廳看新聞。<br />\n他看到我，然後哭。<br />\n<br />\n我看著電視，警總外人潮如鯽。<br />\n我心情忐忑，學生的訴求其實也是警察的訴求：<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會，還前線警員一個清白。<br />\n政府只要一聲令下，他便可以回家。<br />\n<br />\nKen說當了五年警察，心累了，想辭職，做一個平凡、正直的人，但要供樓。<br />\n我希望看到他一展愁顏，但無情的政府，似乎卻要讓他抱恨終身......</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:27:09.000Z","msg":"但要供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b51f9a580f3d5dccb3ce1a75a4eedc5001655da","tid":1249333,"uid":232863,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:29:40.000Z","msg":"大家岩用就拎去喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xu0Q3q4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXu0Q3q4.jpg&h=2eb5292e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6dfadeab6f205eba769cad15af58234a803201e","tid":1249333,"uid":196006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893c626f09b5c9c94e45b52de073ea1c51aaf3f2","tid":1249333,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScncxkJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht